---+ Change password
   * Two options:
      * Change it via the dedicated [[https://wiki.ukp.informatik.tu-darmstadt.de/pwchange/index.pl][password change webpage]].
      * Or if your workstation is in the UKP domain, simply use the =passwd= command on the command line.
   * It might take several minutes until all machines and services accept the new password. Please be patient.
      <!--* Alternatively log in via ssh to any of our compute servers and use =passwd= on the command line there-->

